Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,welcome to soteriology.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:09.59,Latin,,0,0,0,,This course deals with the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,and the doctrine of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:14.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,how the Holy Spirit works in the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:18.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,Running all the way from His effectual calling,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,and regeneration,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,all the way to glorification.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,So it's a very important subject
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:31.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,and I'm glad you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:35.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,We're going to look at it in some detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,I think you'll enjoy the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:41.17,Latin,,0,0,0,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,all of our
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:45.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,Christianity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,all of our personal religion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:51.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,is just a sham without the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,So we're very,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:56.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,very grateful for the ministry of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,I want to begin this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,first lecture with the reading of God's word,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,as we will with each each lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.68,Latin,,0,0,0,,Turn with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:10.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,please,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:14.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,to Romans 8 and I'll read 13 through 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,Romans 8: 13 through 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,For,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,if you live after the flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:25.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,you shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,But if ye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:29.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,through the Spirit do mortify,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,the deeds of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:34.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,ye shall live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.17,Latin,,0,0,0,,For as many as are led
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the Spirit of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,they are the sons of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,For you have not received the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,of bondage again to fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:52.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,but you have received the Spirit of adoption
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,whereby we cry Abba,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:56.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:01.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Spirit itself beareth witness with our spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we are the children of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,and if children then heirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:10.00,Latin,,0,0,0,,heirs of God and joint heirs with Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,If so be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we suffer with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:19.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,that we may also be glorified together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,Let's seek God's face in prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,Lord God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,we stand on holy ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:32.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,as we approach this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:37.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,immense subject of the third person of the Holy Trinity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:42.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,and his salvific work in our souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,And we do pray that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.49,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the end of this course,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,we will have a much more profound appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:55.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,for the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,than we perhaps might have at present
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help us to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:05.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,not only in the grace and knowledge of Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,whom the Spirit focuses upon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,but also that we would grow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:16.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the grace and knowledge of the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,becoming more aware of His work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,His saving work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,and appreciating more profoundly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,the vastness of His ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,as he works in sinners and rebels,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:36.32,Latin,,0,0,0,,such as we all are by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,So Lord bless this class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help me in teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,Help the students in listening,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,learning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,and grant that each lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,may serve to thy glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:57.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,to our spiritual growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to the well-being
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.79,Latin,,0,0,0,,of our entire being as we journey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,to the never-ending eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,Be with us now we pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,In Jesus name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,thank you for joining us for this class
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,and I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:25.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,begin with the first lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:27.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is titled: The Study
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Study of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:40.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,God's Holy spirit was with God's people from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,Already in Genesis 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,verse 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:50.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,leading them ultimately to their rest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:57.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,in Jesus Christ (Isaiah 63 14)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,To know the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,therefore is to stand in continuity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,with the Saints of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,God has promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,his Spirit already to Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,His chosen people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,We know that in the Old Testament,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:24.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,various individuals experience a comfort of that Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.98,Latin,,0,0,0,,Think of David,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,for example (Psalm 51)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,But God promised
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.71,Latin,,0,0,0,,a far richer and broader work of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:40.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,than we might possibly imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,Isaiah foretold of a righteous king
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.23,Latin,,0,0,0,,whose administration would be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.00,Latin,,0,0,0,,rivers of waters in a dry place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,and the transformation of the barren wilderness
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:59.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,into a world filled with the fruit of righteousness (Isaiah 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,When the Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,When the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,is poured out upon us from on high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,And then he goes on to say in Isaiah 44,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.88,Latin,,0,0,0,,that the Spirit would be poured out on Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,like a river
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,of water on dry ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:24.02,Latin,,0,0,0,,irrigating faithless souls to produce a people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:28.17,Latin,,0,0,0,,who say I am the Lord's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.94,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:35.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the answer of God's covenantal faithfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,to the chronic problem
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,of Israel's covenant breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,You find that also in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,the Book of Joel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:50.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,that the Lord would pour out his Spirit upon all his people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,that whosoever would call on the name
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Lord would be saved
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:07:01.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,(Joel 2:28 to 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:05.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,So to study the work of the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,is to study heavenly work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,And work that abides forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the New Testament age you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,that when Jesus rose from the dead
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.77,Latin,,0,0,0,,and ascended into heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,He poured out His Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.57,Latin,,0,0,0,,in much larger measures than
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,had previously been known
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,(Acts 2 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,through 21 and 33 and 34)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:48.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,And Peter after his sermon is interrupted by
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,thousands of people who are under great conviction of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,Under it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,and they cried out men and Brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,Peter said to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,repent and be baptized everyone of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the name of Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:12.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,And you shall receive the gift of the Holy Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,For the promise is unto you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to your children
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,and to all that are afar off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:23.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,Even as many as the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:28.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,Our God shall call (Acts 2: 38 and 39).
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so the rest
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.63,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the New Testament writings,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,particularly Paul's Epistles,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,are just filled with the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,He speaks often
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,about being born
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit such as Galatians,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,4: 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.16,Latin,,0,0,0,,And he's talking constantly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,about different aspects
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit's saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,Like we just read a few
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.49,Latin,,0,0,0,,of them to you from from Romans 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:09.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,So if we treasure Christ as our only mediator,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,we will also treasure the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,as Christ's great gift,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is inseparable from Him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,to sinners (John 4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,and again John 7).
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.69,Latin,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Edwards put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,"The sum of the blessings Christ sought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,by what he did and suffered
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,in the work of redemption,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,was the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,the Holy Spirit in His indwelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,His influences and fruits
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:49.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the sum of all grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,holiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,comfort and joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,or in one word
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:58.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,of all the spiritual good Christ purchased
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.04,Latin,,0,0,0,,for men in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,And is also the sum of all perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.71,Latin,,0,0,0,,glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,and eternal joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,that he purchased
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,for them in another world."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,That's an amazing quote by Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,And it certainly shows us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,that many today are minimizing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,the role of the ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Holy Spirit as
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,integral with the entire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,sum of blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,that God's people receive in salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,John Brown of Headington
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,put it this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,"Did Christ purchase the Holy Spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,Christ purchased the Spirit's gifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,and influences in applying redemption,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.11,Latin,,0,0,0,,but not his being,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,which is independent."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,So the work of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:04.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,in many ways
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,is the fruit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,of Christ's death and resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.63,Latin,,0,0,0,,salvation in Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,is appreciated and enjoyed therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.33,Latin,,0,0,0,,only by knowing the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,and his saving work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,And this is one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,greatest doctrines of the Reformation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:32.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,developed so thoroughly and then even
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,augmented by the Puritans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,What a treasure Reformed theology brings us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,about the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.32,Latin,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,BB Warfield called John Calvin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,The Theologian of the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,And Warfield went on to claim
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,the developed doctrine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the work of the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,is an exclusively Reformation doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:08.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,and more particularly a Reformed doctrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,and still more particularly a Puritan doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,study of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:22.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,through Reformed experiential soteriology,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.72,Latin,,0,0,0,,- that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,salvation that we experience
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,by the work
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,of the Spirit in the soul -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:34.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,opens up a vast wealth of wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,and joy to the believer.
